translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,"Jab Moosa ne muddat poori kardi aur woh apne ehal-o-aayal(family) ko lekar chala to Toor ki jaanib usko ek aag nazar aayi.Usne apne ghar walon se kaha “thehro, maine ek aag dekhi hai, shayad main wahan se koi khabar le aaoon ya is aag se koi angara hi utha laaon jissey tum taap sako.”"
  28,30,"Wahan pahuncha to wadi ke dahine kinarey par mubarak khittey mein ek darakht se pukara gaya ke “Aey Moosa, main hi Allah hoon, sarey jahaan walon ka maalik”"
  28,31,"Aur (hukum diya gaya ke) “phenk de apni laathi.”Junhi ke Moosa ne dekha ke woh laathi saanp (snake) ki tarah bal kha rahi hai to woh peeth pher kar bhaaga aur unse mudh kar bhi na dekha. (Irshad hua) “Moosa, palat aa aur khauf na kar, tu bilkul mehfuz hai"
  28,32,"Apna haath girehban mein daal, chamakta hua niklega bagair kisi takleef ke aur khauf se bachne ke liye apna baazu bhench le(fold back). Yeh do roshan nishaniyan hain tere Rubb ki taraf se Firoun aur uske darbariyon ke saamne pesh karne ke liye, woh badey hi nafarmaan log hain”"
  28,33,"Moosa ne arz kiya “Mere aaqa, main to unka ek aadmi qatal kar chuka hoon, darta hoon ke woh mujhey maar daalenge"
  28,34,"Aur mera bhai Haroon mujhse zyada zubaan awar (eloquent of tongue) hai, usey mere saath madadgaar ke taur par bhej taa-ke woh meri taaeed (support) karey, mujhey andesha hai ke woh log mujhey jhutlayenge.”"
  28,35,Farmaya “hum tere bhai ke zariye se tera haath mazboot karenge aur tum dono ko aisi sitwat(authority) bakshenge ke woh tumhara kuch na bigaad sakenge.Hamari nishaniyon ke zoar se galaba (triumph) tumhare aur tumhare pairawon ka hi hoga”